text: Taza is a city in Morocco. Taza may also refer to: *Taza (crater), on Mars *Taza (Iraq), a town in Iraq *Taza (Lydia), a town of ancient Lydia, now in Turkey *Taza (film), 1954 American western a/k/a Taza, Son of Cochise *Chief Taza, an Apache leader *Taza National Park, in Algeria
title: Taza (disambiguation)
